{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 532.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We should actually make the escape 15 minutes earlier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we should escape in an orderly manner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was planned that we should assemble in normal walking groups and march to the main gate, because Sobibor, when you go in, had little like cages and cages.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was cage, surrounded by barbed-wires, where we used to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In another cage, we used to walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And gates lead from one cage to another one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the plan was that we march out, like, like, it would be a German order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we'd march to the main gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were hoping that the guards will think it's a German order, because we go so brazenly straight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we would come close to the gate, where the machine gun is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they will see that something is not OK, the guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It will be too late for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we will overwhelm them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It didn't happen, just because we were discovered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "How it happened, I will tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] October 13, I remember, about 3 o'clock, I heard some laughing, shooting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I was afraid that we were discovered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But what's happened-- a group of Nazis that come from the nearby camp of Osada just to have a good drink, you know, because they had a  lot of liquor in Sobibor, but because there were more Germans, now, the escape was called off for the 13th and was set for the next day.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The next day, I was scared that we will be betrayed, again, in some way, because we were once.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't tell you the story, but we were once betrayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a long story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did later become the oberkapo, the traitor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we killed him later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We poisoned him.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
